    "stage": "Reading for writing",
    "stageLabel": "写作篇",
    "unitNumber": 4,
    "unitTheme": "The art of having fun",
    "bookId": "g7b",
    "bookLabel": "七年级下册",
    "bookShortLabel": "7下",
    "bookOrder": 241,
    "summary": "识别吞噬时间的娱乐陷阱，学习保持有节制的快乐。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s1",
      "text": "Have you ever noticed a monster around us?",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p1",
      "tr": "你有没有注意到我们身边有一个怪兽？",
      "g": "现在完成时态疑问句",
      "d": "Have you ever done...? 意为“你曾经做过...吗？”",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/g7ytepJN7GSMjd2yUKLZei.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s2",
      "text": "It's not big or scary, but it's very dangerous.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p1",
      "tr": "它并不高大也不可怕，但它非常危险。",
      "g": "并列复合句结构",
      "d": "but 连接两个分句，表示转折。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/CKE4qxmLq74Dxz34ZK235U.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s3",
      "text": "This monster comes in many forms – games, social media and TV shows.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p1",
      "tr": "这个怪兽以多种形式出现——游戏、社交媒体和电视节目。",
      "g": "主语+谓语+状语结构",
      "d": "come in many forms 以多种形式出现。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/XfimvMjeWCXrU6cR82KgMA.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s4",
      "text": "You may ask, “It brings us so much fun.”",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p1",
      "tr": "你可能会问：“它带给我们这么多乐趣。”",
      "g": "主语+谓语+宾语结构",
      "d": "may 表示推测；bring sb. sth. 给某人带来某物。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/suQ9EdjHruLidCNKtM46fG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s5",
      "text": "So why do you say it’s a monster?",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p1",
      "tr": "那你为什么说它是怪兽呢？",
      "g": "特殊疑问句结构",
      "d": "why 引导特殊疑问句，询问原因。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/kP3FNumgePhw2TQXi76eHF.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s6",
      "text": "At first, we may all think, “I’ll just have a little fun.”",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p2",
      "tr": "起初，我们可能都会想：“我只是想玩一会儿。”",
      "g": "直接引语结构",
      "d": "At first 意为“起初”；have a little fun 玩一会儿。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/aQAQGdcYM9AB73Unk7A54P.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s7",
      "text": "We turn on the computer and start a game.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p2",
      "tr": "我们打开电脑，开始玩游戏。",
      "g": "并列谓语结构",
      "d": "turn on 意为“打开（电器等）”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/FyhJ2D99o54ciGGLUrK44f.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s8",
      "text": "But soon the monster takes over.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p2",
      "tr": "但很快怪兽就接管了。",
      "g": "主语+谓语结构",
      "d": "take over 意为“接管，控制”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ZTh4Vipmh8TXRgdQbFDGYK.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s9",
      "text": "It starts to eat away our time, minute by minute.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p2",
      "tr": "它开始一分钟一分钟地吞噬我们的时间。",
      "g": "主语+谓语+宾语结构",
      "d": "start to do sth. 开始做某事；minute by minute 一分钟一分钟地。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/pzZh3R7DZRekq4su3Fhvmi.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s10",
      "text": "But we just sit there and look at the screen without noticing it at all.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p2",
      "tr": "但我们只是坐在那里盯着屏幕，完全没有注意到它。",
      "g": "并列复合句结构",
      "d": "without doing sth. 意为“没有做某事”；not...at all 一点也不。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/3armZPvR9pBQrW3HgBKYFk.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s11",
      "text": "We often get lost in the monster’s world like this.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p2",
      "tr": "我们就这样经常迷失在怪兽的世界里。",
      "g": "主语+系动词+表语结构",
      "d": "get lost 意为“迷失”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/dVd4qZyp4dRXhwSkrzNyb3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s12",
      "text": "We become couch potatoes with sore necks and dry eyes.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p3",
      "tr": "我们变成了脖子酸痛、眼睛干涩的“电视迷”。",
      "g": "主语+系动词+表语结构",
      "d": "couch potato 意为“整天坐在沙发上看电视的人”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/xkFFMxb42AJ7YcCRXmgeCc.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s13",
      "text": "We miss out on sweet moments with loved ones.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p3",
      "tr": "我们错过了与亲人在一起的甜蜜时刻。",
      "g": "主语+谓语+宾语结构",
      "d": "miss out on 意为“错过”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/VQxso78gHL3FTHvw5TWd98.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s14",
      "text": "We are deaf to the real world.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p3",
      "tr": "我们对现实世界充耳不闻。",
      "g": "主语+系动词+表语结构",
      "d": "be deaf to 意为“对...充耳不闻”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/gaDaie4SJQDKN8TJLsFVyP.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s15",
      "text": "Just remember, too much fun also makes Jack a dull boy!",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p4",
      "tr": "记住，过度娱乐也会让孩子变傻！",
      "g": "祈使句结构",
      "d": "too much 意为“太多”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/WQGbTNWUzH3mRdQrdkKe9Q.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s16",
      "text": "The time-eating monster will always be there.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p4",
      "tr": "时间怪兽永远都在那里。",
      "g": "主语+谓语+状语结构",
      "d": "will always be 意为“将永远是”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/3XhatGqVmgjAfhvkiPGUYf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s17",
      "text": "But we can keep it away by having fun in a balanced way.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p4",
      "tr": "但我们可以通过平衡的娱乐方式让它远离。",
      "g": "主语+谓语+宾语结构",
      "d": "keep...away 意为“使...远离”；by doing sth. 通过做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/dXkt3gNokoua3PF5Tw8cMV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s18",
      "text": "So, stand up and leave the screens!",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p5",
      "tr": "所以，站起来，离开屏幕！",
      "g": "祈使句结构",
      "d": "stand up 站起来；leave 离开。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/MBuV7AKLnXYSkVDPFT4wEV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s19",
      "text": "Go outside, feel the sun on your face, and jog in the fresh air.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p5",
      "tr": "去户外，感受阳光洒在脸上，在清新的空气中慢跑。",
      "g": "祈使句结构",
      "d": "feel the sun 感受阳光；fresh air 清新的空气。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/rSDMc36de7sBaJZVmgCceR.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s20",
      "text": "Play tennis or go hiking with your friends.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p5",
      "tr": "和朋友一起打网球或徒步旅行。",
      "g": "祈使句结构",
      "d": "go hiking 去徒步；with your friends 和你的朋友。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/RweRpw2PQeiB4iYLNpfLTm.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s21",
      "text": "Talk about your day with your family.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p5",
      "tr": "和家人聊聊你的一天。",
      "g": "祈使句结构",
      "d": "talk about 谈论；your day 你的一天。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/DE245vAno3NCqMrSFZVoZe.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s22",
      "text": "There is so much for you to do.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p5",
      "tr": "你有这么多事情可以做。",
      "g": "存在句 (There be) 结构",
      "d": "There is so much for you to do. 有很多事等着你去做。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/vUfNJpw8KtCFURKtTtMBsT.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-article-s23",
      "text": "The choice is ours.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-article-p5",
      "tr": "选择权在我们手中。",
      "g": "主语+系动词+表语结构",
      "d": "ours 是名词性物主代词，意为“我们的”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/cwDBPpkjUnc8QMkThbj9MJ.mp3"
    }
  ],
